WEBVTT

00:08.384 --> 00:11.011
- I'M RAISING FIVE KIDS,
AND I DIDN'T MISS LAST WEEK.

00:11.011 --> 00:12.471
WHAT'S YOUR EXCUSE?

00:12.471 --> 00:13.806
SHUT THE FUCK UP!

00:13.806 --> 00:15.391
I NEED YOU
TO GET A WILL NOTARIZED.

00:15.391 --> 00:17.227
- WILL?
- AUNT GINGER'S.

00:17.227 --> 00:18.477
- A WILL'S NO GOOD
WITHOUT A DEATH CERTIFICATE.

00:18.477 --> 00:20.063
- YEAH, WE'RE GONNA NEED
A BODY TOO.

00:20.063 --> 00:21.939
- A REAL LIVE BODY?
- NOT LIVE.

00:21.939 --> 00:23.315
- I'M HERE TO FILE A WILL,
PLEASE.

00:23.315 --> 00:25.317
- GINGER GALLAGHER.
SECOND ONE TODAY.

00:25.317 --> 00:26.861
SUPERSEDES YOURS.

00:26.861 --> 00:29.321
- WHO THE HELL FILED IT?
COUSIN PATRICK.

00:29.321 --> 00:31.323
both: ARE YOU OUT
OF YOUR FUCKING MIND?

00:31.323 --> 00:33.617
- KEV IS JUST GONNA LIE DOWN
WITH YOU FOR PROCREATION.

00:33.617 --> 00:35.161
- OKAY, LET'S GET THIS GOING.

00:35.161 --> 00:37.371
- [laughs]
- SHH, KNOCK IT OFF, MAMA.

00:37.371 --> 00:39.165
- HOW MANY MORE TIMES
ARE WE GONNA HAVE TO DO THIS?

00:39.165 --> 00:40.583
- UNTIL WE COMPLETE
THE MISSION.

00:40.583 --> 00:42.085
- YOU GUYS LOOK LIKE
YOU COULD USE SOME HELP.

00:42.085 --> 00:43.169
- YOU CAN GO HOME.

00:43.169 --> 00:44.795
- YOU KNOW WHAT?
HAVE HER STICK AROUND.

00:44.795 --> 00:46.338
I GOT TO HIT THE ALIBI
IN TEN MINUTES ANYWAY.

00:46.338 --> 00:48.007
- I'M GOOD TO STAY.
- PLEASE JUST GO HOME

00:48.007 --> 00:49.800
TO YOUR OWN
FUCKING HOUSE FOR ONCE.

00:49.800 --> 00:51.927
- YOU MIND IF I MAKE
ONE OF THESE OUT TO CASH?

00:51.927 --> 00:53.679
NOTHING BIG,
JUST SOME WALKING AROUND MONEY.

00:53.679 --> 00:55.681
- JOINT BANK ACCOUNT
IS FOR IMMIGRATION ONLY.

00:55.681 --> 00:58.101
- HAVE A HEART.
I'M TAPPED.

00:58.101 --> 01:00.478
- MOM.
- OH!

01:00.478 --> 01:02.230
- WHERE IS HE, MY BABY?

01:02.230 --> 01:04.899
- HE'S WHERE
HE BELONGS FOR NOW,

01:04.899 --> 01:07.234
AND YOU'RE BACK
WHERE YOU BELONG.

01:07.234 --> 01:10.571
- NOW, IF I ALLOW YOU
TO RETAIN YOUR PARENTAL RIGHTS,

01:10.571 --> 01:13.199
WOULD YOU CONSENT TO
YOUR DAUGHTER BECOMING GUARDIAN?

01:13.199 --> 01:14.700
- WORKS FOR ME.

01:14.700 --> 01:17.286
- WOULD YOU AGREE TO BE
THE GUARDIAN OF THESE CHILDREN?

01:17.286 --> 01:19.538
- YES, I DO.

01:27.671 --> 01:30.674
[High Strung's
The Luck You Got]

01:30.674 --> 01:34.678
♪ ♪

01:34.678 --> 01:37.973
- ♪ THINK OF ALL THE LUCK
YOU GOT ♪

01:37.973 --> 01:40.976
♪ KNOW THAT
IT'S NOT FOR NAUGHT ♪

01:40.976 --> 01:44.188
♪ YOU WERE BEAMING
ONCE BEFORE ♪

01:44.188 --> 01:48.817
♪ BUT IT'S NOT LIKE THAT
ANYMORE ♪

01:48.817 --> 01:52.197
♪ WHAT IS THIS DOWNSIDE ♪

01:52.197 --> 01:55.407
♪ THAT YOU SPEAK OF? ♪

01:55.407 --> 01:57.535
♪ WHAT IS THIS FEELING ♪

01:57.535 --> 02:00.704
♪ YOU'RE SO SURE OF? ♪

02:00.704 --> 02:09.297
♪ ♪

02:09.297 --> 02:12.300
♪ ROUND UP THE FRIENDS
YOU GOT ♪

02:12.300 --> 02:15.594
♪ KNOW THAT
THEY'RE NOT FOR NAUGHT ♪

02:15.594 --> 02:18.597
♪ YOU WERE WILLING
ONCE BEFORE ♪

02:18.597 --> 02:23.353
♪ BUT IT'S NOT LIKE THAT
ANYMORE ♪

02:23.353 --> 02:26.438
♪ WHAT IS THIS DOWNSIDE ♪

02:26.438 --> 02:30.235
♪ THAT YOU SPEAK OF? ♪

02:30.235 --> 02:32.237
♪ WHAT IS THIS FEELING ♪

02:32.237 --> 02:36.865
♪ YOU'RE SO SURE OF? ♪

02:36.865 --> 02:40.744
- THANK YOU ALL FOR COMING OUT
IN HONOR OF AUNT GINGER.

02:40.744 --> 02:43.247
"G.G." AS I CALLED HER.

02:43.247 --> 02:44.957
YOU NOW, WHEN THE GUY
AT THE FUNERAL PLACE

02:44.957 --> 02:46.250
HANDED ME HER ASHES,
I THOUGHT,

02:46.250 --> 02:47.918
WHAT THE HELL
DO I DO WITH THESE?

02:47.918 --> 02:50.671
PUT 'EM IN A VASE
ON MY MANTLE?

02:50.671 --> 02:52.506
OR SCATTER THEM
AT THE PARK OR THE LAKE?

02:52.506 --> 02:55.175
THEN I THOUGHT, NO,

02:55.175 --> 02:57.970
I KNOW WHERE
SHE WAS HAPPIEST.

02:57.970 --> 03:01.224
ON THIS CORNER,
HER CORNER,

03:01.224 --> 03:03.517
WHERE SHE TURNED TRICKS
IN HER 20s AND 30s.

03:03.517 --> 03:05.019
- AND 60s!

03:05.019 --> 03:08.439
- SHE DID MAGIC TRICKS?
- NO, NO, NO, SON.

03:08.439 --> 03:11.066
"TURNING TRICKS" IS
A EUPHEMISM FOR PROSTITUTION.

03:11.066 --> 03:13.736
IN HER DAY, YOUR GREAT AUNT WAS
A LEGENDARY POLE SMOKER.

03:13.736 --> 03:16.864
COULD UNLOCK HER JAW
LIKE A BURMESE PYTHON.

03:16.864 --> 03:18.782
- WE ARE AT HER FUNERAL.

03:18.782 --> 03:20.242
- YOU KNOW,
SOME THINK GALLAGHERS

03:20.242 --> 03:22.119
DON'T HAVE A WORK ETHIC,

03:22.119 --> 03:25.581
BUT GINGER WORKED THIS CORNER
RAIN, SLEET, SNOW,

03:25.581 --> 03:27.374
HER OLD KNEES HITTING
THAT HARD PAVEMENT

03:27.374 --> 03:29.252
AGAIN AND AGAIN.

03:29.252 --> 03:33.255
BERTIE GIDDELMAN IS THE ONLY ONE
THAT'S OUTLASTED HER.

03:33.255 --> 03:36.258
- LOOK, YOU ALL KNEW GINGER,
SO I AIN'T GONNA SUGARCOAT IT.

03:36.258 --> 03:38.303
SHE WAS A MEAN OLD BITCH.

03:38.303 --> 03:41.930
BUT EVEN A MEAN OLD BITCH
DESERVES A SEND OFF.

03:41.930 --> 03:43.433
- HERE, HERE.

03:43.433 --> 03:44.808
- SO THIS IS US, GINGER,

03:44.808 --> 03:50.440
SENDING YOU OFF,
RIGHT WHERE YOU BELONG.

03:52.399 --> 03:53.734
- IT'S TOUCHING.

03:53.734 --> 03:55.569
- I'M TEARING UP.

03:55.569 --> 03:57.322
- OKAY, KIDS, LET'S GO.

03:57.322 --> 03:59.156
- PATRICK.

03:59.156 --> 04:01.325
SO GINGER HAD A WILL
THAT WE DIDN'T KNOW ABOUT,

04:01.325 --> 04:03.827
AND YOU JUST HAD IT SITTING
IN A DRAWER?

04:03.827 --> 04:05.455
- YEP.

04:05.455 --> 04:07.415
- AND EVEN THOUGH
SHE HATED YOUR GUTS,

04:07.415 --> 04:08.415
SHE LEFT OUR HOUSE TO YOU?

04:08.415 --> 04:10.209
- IT WAS NEVER YOUR HOUSE.

04:10.209 --> 04:11.877
- IT'S WEIRD, YOU KNOW,

04:11.877 --> 04:13.629
HOW SHE SIGNED THE WILL
ONLY A YEAR AGO,

04:13.629 --> 04:15.130
YOU KNOW, HER BEING
AN INVALID AND ALL.

04:15.130 --> 04:16.882
- SIGNED AND NOTARIZED.

04:16.882 --> 04:18.591
- I DON'T REMEMBER YOU
COMING BY WITH A LAWYER.

04:18.591 --> 04:20.010
- I GOTTA GET BACK
TO MY FAMILY.

04:20.010 --> 04:21.678
- SIX KIDS
WITH NOWHERE ELSE TO GO.

04:21.678 --> 04:23.473
- WHY DON'T
WE TALK ABOUT THIS

04:23.473 --> 04:25.391
WHEN THE STING OF LOSING GINGER
HAS WORN OFF, HMM?

04:25.391 --> 04:27.559
TOMORROW, MAYBE?

04:33.816 --> 04:37.986
- YOU WANT TO TELL THEM
OR SHOULD I?

04:37.986 --> 04:42.199
- V, YOUR MOM'S HERE.

04:42.199 --> 04:43.867
OOH.
YOU LOOK REALLY NICE, CAROL.

04:43.867 --> 04:45.786
- THANK YOU, HONEY.
- YOU DO LOOK NICE.

04:45.786 --> 04:48.539
WHERE'D YOU GET THAT DRESS?
- MADISON'S.

04:48.539 --> 04:50.375
- AND THOSE SHOES.

04:50.375 --> 04:51.375
YOU DOING SOMETHING
AT CHURCH LATER?

04:51.375 --> 04:53.669
- I'M OVULATING AGAIN.

04:53.669 --> 04:55.546
- OVULATING?

04:55.546 --> 04:57.507
NO, IT'S NOT UNTIL NEXT WEEK.
I GOT THE CALENDAR.

04:57.507 --> 04:59.007
- HIGH BODY TEMPERATURE,
SORE BREASTS,

04:59.007 --> 05:00.467
INCREASED CERVICAL MUCUS.

05:00.467 --> 05:01.927
- WE BELIEVE YOU, MAMA.

05:01.927 --> 05:03.345
- WELL, IF YOU ALL WANT
TO TRY AGAIN,

05:03.345 --> 05:06.640
WE HAVE A FOUR-DAY WINDOW.

05:06.640 --> 05:09.143
- GUESS NO NEED TO WASTE
AN OPPORTUNITY, RIGHT, BABY?

05:09.143 --> 05:11.479
- WHAT, YOU WANNA DO THIS
RIGHT NOW?

05:11.479 --> 05:12.354
LIKE, RIGHT NOW?

05:12.354 --> 05:13.939
- WELL, I CAN COME BACK.

05:13.939 --> 05:15.983
- NO, NO NEED.

05:15.983 --> 05:17.776
I'M LIKE A STUD BULL.

05:17.776 --> 05:19.945
YOU OPEN THE BARN DOOR,
SLAP ME ON THE ASS.

05:19.945 --> 05:22.322
YOU KNOW, I MEAN, WHEN I SAY,
"OPEN THE BARN DOOR,"

05:22.322 --> 05:25.325
I DON'T MEAN YOUR, UM--

05:25.325 --> 05:27.202
UH, DO YOU GUYS
WANT A DRINK?

05:27.202 --> 05:29.414
- I'LL GET THREE GLASSES.

05:32.207 --> 05:33.584
- ARE YOU SURE YOU JUST WANT
TO JUMP INTO THIS?

05:33.584 --> 05:35.127
YOU DON'T WANT A MINUTE
TO THINK?

05:35.127 --> 05:36.920
- WAITING ISN'T GONNA
MAKE IT EASIER.

05:36.920 --> 05:38.505
- ALL RIGHT, I'M GONNA
BLOCK EVERYTHING OUT,

05:38.505 --> 05:40.424
AND I'M JUST GONNA PICTURE
YOUR BEAUTIFUL FACE.

05:40.424 --> 05:43.969
- I PICTURE DENZEL WASHINGTON.
- OH, FOR REAL?

05:43.969 --> 05:47.389
- WHEN I OPEN MY EYES A LITTLE
AND I SEE IT'S A WHITE GUY,

05:47.389 --> 05:49.850
EH, THEN I GO
WITH JOHNNY DEPP.

05:49.850 --> 05:51.226
- OH?

05:51.226 --> 05:53.520
- YOU APPRECIATE THE IRONY,
RIGHT?

05:53.520 --> 05:56.440
SENSELESS ARGUMENTS ABOUT
WHO GETS WHAT BEDROOM,

05:56.440 --> 05:58.734
REFUSING TO ALLOW ME TO STAY.

05:58.734 --> 06:02.362
NOW, NOBODY GETS TO STAY.
- WHY IS FRANK HERE AGAIN?

06:02.362 --> 06:03.906
- THERE'S A SMALL CHANCE
HE'LL BE ABLE TO HELP

06:03.906 --> 06:06.492
SINCE HE'S KNOWN PATRICK
LONGER THAN ANY OF US.

06:06.492 --> 06:08.076
- PATRICK WANTS
TO STEAL OUR HOUSE?

06:08.076 --> 06:09.537
- HE'S A CONTRACTOR.
HE'S GONNA FLIP IT.

06:09.537 --> 06:10.579
SLAP A COAT OF PAINT ON IT,

06:10.579 --> 06:12.956
CALL IT
"A COZY, AUTHENTIC PRE-WAR,"

06:12.956 --> 06:14.041
AND OFFLOAD IT TO YUPPIES.

06:14.041 --> 06:15.793
- NOT GONNA HAPPEN.

06:15.793 --> 06:17.544
SO LET'S GO OVER OUR OPTIONS.
- I'LL WRITE THEM DOWN.

06:17.544 --> 06:19.546
- ALL RIGHT, LOOK, WE KNOW
THE WILL IS BULLSHIT.

06:19.546 --> 06:21.256
IT WAS SIGNED A YEAR AGO,

06:21.256 --> 06:23.217
AND GINGER'S
BEEN DEAD FOR WHAT, 10?

06:23.217 --> 06:24.760
- MORE LIKE 15.

06:24.760 --> 06:27.596
- OPTION ONE:
PROVE WILL IS A FORGERY.

06:27.596 --> 06:29.848
- WE CAN'T CALL THE COPS
BECAUSE WE FAKED GINGER'S DEATH

06:29.848 --> 06:31.809
AND FORGED A WILL OF OUR OWN.

06:31.809 --> 06:34.394
- PLUS FRANK'S BEEN CASHING
GINGER'S SOCIAL SECURITY CHECKS.

06:34.394 --> 06:37.022
- OH, LIKE YOU DIDN'T SHARE
IN THAT BOUNTY?

06:37.022 --> 06:38.732
- WHAT WE COULD DO,
WE COULD ARGUE

06:38.732 --> 06:41.569
THAT GINGER WASN'T OF
SOUND MIND WHEN SHE SIGNED IT.

06:41.569 --> 06:43.612
I MEAN, SHE WAS
NEVER OF SOUND MIND ANYWAY.

06:43.612 --> 06:47.492
- OPTION TWO:
SAY GINGER WAS CRAZY.

06:47.492 --> 06:49.493
- OR CONVINCE PATRICK
TO BACK OFF SOMEHOW.

06:49.493 --> 06:50.702
- YEAH, THAT'S THREE.

06:50.702 --> 06:52.120
- GOOD LUCK WITH THAT!

06:52.120 --> 06:53.580
HIS NICKNAME
USED TO BE PIT BULL.

06:53.580 --> 06:55.499
IT WAS PARTLY AN ODOR THING,

06:55.499 --> 06:57.709
BUT ALSO BECAUSE ONCE HE GETS
AHOLD OF YOU, HE DOESN'T LET GO.

06:57.709 --> 06:59.294
YOU GOTTA KILL HIM FIRST.

06:59.294 --> 07:01.631
- OPTION FOUR: KILL PATRICK.

07:01.631 --> 07:03.048
- IT'S TIME TO FACE REALITY.

07:03.048 --> 07:05.217
PATRICK OUT-GALLAGHERED US,

07:05.217 --> 07:07.928
AND THERE'S NO POINT
IN FIGHTING IT.

07:07.928 --> 07:09.763
- EASY FOR YOU TO SAY,
YOU'RE AT SHEILA'S.

07:09.763 --> 07:11.390
- SO BEFORE YOU'RE OUT
ON THE STREETS

07:11.390 --> 07:14.852
LIKE SO MANY SOMALIAN REFUGEES,
ASK YOURSELVES,

07:14.852 --> 07:17.855
"IF PATRICK
IS TAKING THE HOUSE,

07:17.855 --> 07:21.108
WHAT ARE WE TAKING?"

07:21.108 --> 07:22.693
COPPER PIPES.

07:22.693 --> 07:24.653
- YOU'RE NOT TAKING THE PIPES,
FRANK.

07:24.653 --> 07:27.532
YOU REALLY THINK THERE'S
A WAY TO CHALLENGE THE WILL?

07:27.532 --> 07:29.616
- WHY NOT? YOU KNOW,
IF I CAN BONE UP ON PROBATE LAW.

07:29.616 --> 07:33.120
- ALL IN FAVOR.

07:33.120 --> 07:34.204
UNANIMOUS.

07:34.204 --> 07:35.581
- WELL, LIKE HELL IT IS.

07:35.581 --> 07:36.623
- LIP WILL HANDLE THE WILL.

07:36.623 --> 07:38.333
THE REST OF YOU,

07:38.333 --> 07:39.585
GET READY FOR THE FIRST DAY
OF SCHOOL TOMORROW.

07:39.585 --> 07:40.836
DEBBIE AND CARL,
PICK OUT SOMETHING TO WEAR

07:40.836 --> 07:42.505
THAT DOESN'T HAVE HOLES.

07:42.505 --> 07:43.631
- WOULDN'T IT JUST BE EASIER
TO KILL HIM?

07:43.631 --> 07:44.590
- CLOTHES, NOW.

07:44.590 --> 07:46.508
WE BETTER WORK FAST.

07:46.508 --> 07:48.760
WINTER'S COMING, AND IT'LL
BE COLD SLEEPING IN THE PARK.

07:48.760 --> 07:51.556
- THIS IS WHY DEMOCRACY
DOES NOT WORK.

07:54.683 --> 07:57.561
- TIME TO GET OUT
THE "HELP WANTED" ADS.

07:57.561 --> 07:59.855
- HOW YOU HOLDING UP?
- YOU KNOW WHAT I WANT?

07:59.855 --> 08:03.693
NOT TO WIN THE LOTTERY OR
GO ON VACATION TO THE CARIBBEAN.

08:03.693 --> 08:05.695
I WANT NORMAL PEOPLE PROBLEMS.

08:05.695 --> 08:07.613
LIKE,
AM I GETTING ENOUGH FIBER?

08:07.613 --> 08:10.073
WHY DID MY FRIEND
SAY THAT INSENSITIVE THING

08:10.073 --> 08:11.825
ABOUT MY WEIGHT?

08:11.825 --> 08:14.828
- WELL, IT'LL WORK OUT,
IT ALWAYS DOES.

08:14.828 --> 08:17.707
- YOU REALIZE ONLY RICH PEOPLE
SAY SHIT LIKE THAT.

08:19.667 --> 08:20.918
- WHAT'S THAT
SUPPOSED TO MEAN?

08:20.918 --> 08:22.712
- THAT WE HAVE NO BACKUP PLAN.

08:22.712 --> 08:23.879
THERE'S NO RUNNING
TO MOM AND DAD.

08:23.879 --> 08:25.505
- AND THAT'S WHAT I DO?

08:25.505 --> 08:27.674
- I'M SAYING NEITHER ONE OF US
HAS A JOB.

08:27.674 --> 08:29.176
ONE WEEK WITH ME
AS THEIR GUARDIAN, ONE,

08:29.176 --> 08:31.386
THEY'RE ABOUT TO BE HOMELESS.

08:31.386 --> 08:32.763
- THEN WE'LL GET JOBS.

08:32.763 --> 08:35.640
I MEAN, THE GALLAGHERS
ARE SURVIVORS, RIGHT?

08:35.640 --> 08:37.602
WE CAN DO THIS.

08:37.602 --> 08:39.269
- WE?

08:39.269 --> 08:42.063
- YOU, ME, WE.

08:45.693 --> 08:47.986
- SINCE WHEN
ARE YOU A LAWYER?

08:47.986 --> 08:49.529
- SINCE NEVER,

08:49.529 --> 08:51.198
WHICH IS WHY I HAVE TO READ UP
ON THIS SHIT.

08:51.198 --> 08:55.578
- HOW 'BOUT
I GIVE YOU A HUMMER,

08:55.578 --> 08:57.747
HELP YOU RELAX?

08:57.747 --> 09:00.624
- I DON'T THINK THAT'S
GONNA HELP MY PRODUCTIVITY.

09:00.624 --> 09:02.668
- YOU CAN MULTITASK.

09:02.668 --> 09:05.921
- ♪ SAID I FIND IT HARD ♪

09:05.921 --> 09:09.508
♪ ♪

09:09.508 --> 09:12.636
- WOULD YOU, UH...

09:12.636 --> 09:14.721
WOULD YOU BE OFFENDED
IF I KEPT WORKING?

09:14.721 --> 09:15.764
[knock at door]

09:15.764 --> 09:17.140
- LIP, CAN WE TALK?

09:17.140 --> 09:18.767
- YEAH, IF YOU CAN TALK
FROM OUT THERE.

09:18.767 --> 09:21.103
- IT'S PRIVATE.

09:24.690 --> 09:25.691
- THIS BETTER BE GOOD.

09:25.691 --> 09:27.651
♪ ♪

09:27.651 --> 09:30.779
- ♪ SOMETIMES WE KNOW ♪

09:30.779 --> 09:33.783
♪ BUT SOMETIMES ♪

09:33.783 --> 09:35.701
♪ OH BABY SOMETIMES ♪

09:35.701 --> 09:38.203
♪ YOU GOTTA GET
WHAT YOU NEED ♪

09:38.203 --> 09:39.955
♪ ♪

09:45.168 --> 09:46.586
- I RANG THE DOORBELL,

09:46.586 --> 09:48.255
BUT IAN HAD ME WAIT OUT HERE.

09:48.255 --> 09:51.383
I DON'T THINK
HE LIKES ME ANYMORE.

09:51.383 --> 09:53.343
- I DON'T THINK
HE EVER LIKED YOU.

09:53.343 --> 09:56.763
- I GOT YOUR MESSAGE.

09:56.763 --> 10:01.601
- RIGHT, THE ONE WHERE I TOLD
YOU TO GO FUCK YOURSELF?

10:01.601 --> 10:04.730
- IT WAS NICE
TO HEAR YOUR VOICE.

10:09.234 --> 10:10.777
- EIFFEL TOWER?

10:10.777 --> 10:14.239
- YEAH, THIS GUY SAID
HE'D TAKE ME TO PARIS,

10:14.239 --> 10:15.658
SO I HAD THIS DONE.

10:15.658 --> 10:18.618
BUT HE TOOK ALL MY MONEY

10:18.618 --> 10:22.497
AND TRIED TO SELL ME
TO A SHEIKH FROM YEMEN.

10:22.497 --> 10:26.626
SO, YEAH, THINGS GOT BAD
FOR A LITTLE WHILE.

10:26.626 --> 10:29.671
BUT ANYWAYS,

10:29.671 --> 10:31.923
I'M--I'M HOME NOW.

10:31.923 --> 10:35.385
- THAT SOUNDS SHITTY.

10:35.385 --> 10:37.095
- IS MANDY INSIDE?

10:37.095 --> 10:39.056
- YEAH.

10:39.056 --> 10:42.684
- SO THAT'S WHY IAN
HAD ME WAIT OUT HERE?

10:42.684 --> 10:45.937
- THAT'D BE MY GUESS.

10:45.937 --> 10:50.693
- ARE YOU HAPPY?

10:50.693 --> 10:52.737
- SURE.

10:52.737 --> 10:57.115
- WELL, GOOD, BECAUSE
I WANT YOU TO BE HAPPY.

10:57.115 --> 10:59.493
YOU DESERVE IT.

10:59.493 --> 11:03.205
- WELL, I--

11:03.205 --> 11:06.625
I BETTER GET BACK.

11:06.625 --> 11:09.961
- YOU LOOK GOOD.

11:09.961 --> 11:12.297
- WELCOME BACK.

11:14.091 --> 11:15.842
- PLUMBER'S APPRENTICE.
I CAN DO THAT.

11:15.842 --> 11:17.886
- YOU HAVE EXPERIENCE?
- I FIXED OUR TOILET.

11:17.886 --> 11:19.137
- YOU SHOOK THE HANDLE.

11:19.137 --> 11:20.722
WELL, HERE'S A GOOD ONE.

11:20.722 --> 11:22.766
BARISTA AT THE COFFEE BEANERY.

11:22.766 --> 11:24.559
SHELLY ESPINOSA WORKS THERE,
MAKES LIKE 20 GRAND.

11:24.559 --> 11:26.937
- A MONTH?
A YEAR?

11:26.937 --> 11:29.773
SHIT.
HOW DO PEOPLE LIVE ON THAT?

11:29.773 --> 11:32.484
- SO THE CLEANING POSSE GUYS
CALLED BACK.

11:32.484 --> 11:34.779
AN EFFLUENT TANK OVERFLOWED
AT THE SLAUGHTERHOUSE.

11:34.779 --> 11:36.739
THEY CAN USE US BOTH.
$14.50 AN HOUR.

11:36.739 --> 11:38.741
- A WHAT TANK?
- EFFLUENT.

11:40.700 --> 11:42.452
- SEE, I TOLD YOU
IT WOULD WORK OUT.

11:42.452 --> 11:47.750
- IT'S SO EXCITING HAVING YOU
BACK IN YOUR OLD ROOM.

11:47.750 --> 11:51.128
- I JUST WISH I HAD SEEN
HYMIE IN HIS CRIB.

11:51.128 --> 11:54.965
- WELL, MRS. WONG
CAN BRING HYMIE BY ANYTIME.

11:54.965 --> 11:56.716
- HOW IS HE?

11:56.716 --> 11:58.260
- HE'S WONDERFUL.

11:58.260 --> 12:01.054
OH MY GOSH,
HE IS SUCH A SWEET BOY.

12:01.054 --> 12:03.808
AND NOW THAT YOU'RE HOME,
I'M SURE THE WONGS

12:03.808 --> 12:05.893
WILL LET US SPEND MORE TIME
WITH HIM.

12:05.893 --> 12:08.061
- I'M NOT SURE I'M READY
FOR THAT YET.

12:08.061 --> 12:12.315
- I KNOW YOU WANT TO BE
INVOLVED IN HYMIE'S LIFE.

12:12.315 --> 12:16.111
IN FACT, I FOUND A FLYER
FOR A SUPPORT GROUP.

12:16.111 --> 12:18.822
- SUPPORT FOR WHAT?

12:18.822 --> 12:21.449
- FOR FAMILIES AFFECTED
WITH DOWN'S SYNDROME.

12:21.449 --> 12:24.536
I THOUGHT IT MIGHT BE A WAY
FOR US TO EDUCATE OURSELVES

12:24.536 --> 12:26.454
ABOUT HYMIE'S NEEDS.

12:26.454 --> 12:28.415
- BE GRATEFUL
THE KID'S NOT HERE.

12:28.415 --> 12:30.167
- BUTT OUT, FRANK!

12:30.167 --> 12:32.127
- CHILDREN IN THE CAMBODIAN
KILLING FIELDS

12:32.127 --> 12:34.462
TURNED THEIR PARENTS
OVER FOR EXECUTION.

12:34.462 --> 12:38.967
A LIFETIME OF DEVOTION,
THAT'S THE LOYALTY IT BUYS YOU.

12:38.967 --> 12:41.595
- WHO WANTS LASAGNA?

12:41.595 --> 12:44.639
OH, KAREN,
PLEASE PUT YOUR PANTS ON.

12:44.639 --> 12:47.434
- WHAT?
IT'S NOT LIKE I'M NAKED.

12:47.434 --> 12:50.687
- I'M IN RECOVERY.
I'M HYPERSENSITIVE.

12:50.687 --> 12:52.063
- THAT'S A GOOD IDEA.

12:52.063 --> 12:53.607
- JODY, THERE'S ONLY THREE
PLATES HERE.

12:53.607 --> 12:55.192
YOU MIGHT WANT TO GET ONE
FOR KAREN.

12:55.192 --> 12:57.903
[mouthing silently]

12:59.821 --> 13:00.989
- I'M GONNA GO MAKE A SALAD.

13:00.989 --> 13:03.116
- OH, GREAT.

13:03.116 --> 13:06.786
- UM...

13:06.786 --> 13:07.996
FRANK.

13:07.996 --> 13:09.664
- UH-HUH?

13:09.664 --> 13:11.959
- HONEY, WE'VE BEEN THROUGH
A LOT TOGETHER.

13:11.959 --> 13:13.919
- THAT WE HAVE, SHEILS,
THAT WE HAVE.

13:13.919 --> 13:16.964
- UM, BUT HYMIE'S GONE,

13:16.964 --> 13:22.510
AND WITH KAREN AND JODY HERE,
IT'S KIND OF A FULL HOUSE.

13:22.510 --> 13:24.179
- WHAT?

13:24.179 --> 13:27.015
NO.
NO, NO, NO, DON'T SAY THAT.

13:27.015 --> 13:29.851
- FRANK, I'M JUST ASKING YOU
TO GO HOME TO YOUR FAMILY.

13:29.851 --> 13:33.730
- MY FAMILY THREW ME OUT WITH
NO REGARD FOR MY WELL-BEING.

13:33.730 --> 13:34.981
DO YOU WANT ME HOMELESS?

13:34.981 --> 13:37.317
DO YOU WANT ME
WANDERING THE STREETS

13:37.317 --> 13:39.444
JUST AS OLD MAN WINTER
WINDS HIS WAY DOWN

13:39.444 --> 13:41.196
FROM THE FROZEN NORTH?

13:41.196 --> 13:44.867
- DON'T YOU HAVE SOMEONE YOU CAN
STAY WITH, LIKE A FRIEND?

13:44.867 --> 13:47.410
- JUST AS I'M GETTING
MY LIFE TOGETHER.

13:47.410 --> 13:49.120
I'M GOING TO A.A.

13:49.120 --> 13:50.872
- YOU GO BECAUSE
A JUDGE ORDERED YOU TO GO.

13:50.872 --> 13:52.040
- SHEILA.

13:52.040 --> 13:54.877
- FRANK, YOU'RE A GOOD MAN,

13:54.877 --> 13:58.713
BUT YOU'VE GOT TO FIND
ANOTHER PLACE TO STAY.

14:03.885 --> 14:06.263
- JESUS, CARL,
THERE'S ENOUGH TO GO AROUND.

14:06.263 --> 14:07.681
WOULD YOU GRAB THE PAPER BAGS?

14:07.681 --> 14:10.600
- IF WE HAVE TO MOVE,
WHERE DO WE GO?

14:10.600 --> 14:11.893
- WE'RE NOT MOVING.

14:11.893 --> 14:13.061
HOW'S IT GOING
WITH GINGER'S WILL?

14:13.061 --> 14:14.312
- WORKING ON IT.

14:14.312 --> 14:15.855
- V, THANKS FOR
TAKING LIAM TODAY.

14:15.855 --> 14:17.440
- I PRETEND HE'S
MY LITTLE BLACK BABY,

14:17.440 --> 14:19.734
AND WHEN HE'S CRANKY AND SMELLY,
I GET TO BRING HIM BACK.

14:19.734 --> 14:21.194
- WHERE IS LIAM?

14:21.194 --> 14:22.862
- TRYING OUT
THE BIG BOY TOILET.

14:22.862 --> 14:25.115
- AND YOU LEFT HIM THERE?

14:29.494 --> 14:32.706
DEBBIE, THAT IS NOT
THE OUTFIT THAT WE PICKED OUT

14:32.706 --> 14:34.916
FOR YOUR FIRST DAY, AND YOU ARE
SO NOT LEAVING HERE IN THAT.

14:34.916 --> 14:37.127
- I BORROWED IT FROM MANDY.
- CLEARLY.

14:37.127 --> 14:40.505
- YOU DO REALIZE THAT
I'M IN MIDDLE SCHOOL NOW, RIGHT?

14:40.505 --> 14:42.882
- YEAH, NOT STRIPPER SCHOOL.
GO CHANGE.

14:42.882 --> 14:45.593
[knocking at door]
SOMEBODY GET THAT.

14:45.593 --> 14:47.304
- MANDY, SHE'S 13.

14:47.304 --> 14:48.931
SHE'S NOT WORKING THE BEDROOM
AT THE MUSTANG RANCH.

14:48.931 --> 14:50.265
- YEAH, LIKE YOU NEVER WORE
A SHORT SKIRT

14:50.265 --> 14:52.517
WHEN YOU WERE HER AGE.

14:52.517 --> 14:56.105
- JEEZ, FI,
SHE'S JUST TRYING TO HELP.

14:56.105 --> 14:58.732
[knocking at door]
I'LL GET IT.

14:58.732 --> 14:59.983
- CAN YOU TAKE
LIAM TOMORROW TOO?

14:59.983 --> 15:01.944
- NOT SURE YET.

15:01.944 --> 15:03.445
THOSE FRUITS OF ISLAM PEOPLE
ON 4th HAVE A FREE DAYCARE.

15:03.445 --> 15:04.863
IF I SAY I HATE WHITEY,

15:04.863 --> 15:06.281
I BET THEY'LL WATCH HIM
FOR A FEW HOURS.

15:06.281 --> 15:08.993
SO IS LIP GETTING SERIOUS
ABOUT MANDY SKANKOVICH?

15:08.993 --> 15:11.036
- NICE.

15:11.036 --> 15:12.746
- OH, SHIT, MANDY, I'M SORRY.

15:12.746 --> 15:16.916
YOU KNOW I WOULD HAVE NEVER
SAID THAT TO YOUR FACE.

15:16.916 --> 15:19.128
SHOULD I APOLOGIZE OR LEAVE?

15:19.128 --> 15:21.463
I'M GONNA LEAVE.

15:21.463 --> 15:25.717
- YOU AND I BOTH KNOW YOU'RE NOT
LEGALLY ENTITLED TO SHIT.

15:25.717 --> 15:27.052
- PATRICK?

15:27.052 --> 15:28.762
- YOU REMEMBER MY SONS,
DESMOND AND WARREN.

15:28.762 --> 15:30.263
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

15:30.263 --> 15:31.890
- OH, JUST A QUICK WALKTHROUGH
TO ASSESS REPAIRS,

15:31.890 --> 15:33.141
SHOULDN'T TAKE TOO LONG.

15:33.141 --> 15:34.893
- IT'D BE QUICKER
IF YOU JUST LEFT.

15:34.893 --> 15:36.603
- YOU'RE THE ONES
THAT ARE GONNA BE LEAVING.

15:36.603 --> 15:38.188
- ASSUMING YOUR BULLSHIT WILL
STANDS UP IN COURT.

15:38.188 --> 15:39.898
- PROBATE HEARING
IS ON THURSDAY.

15:39.898 --> 15:41.107
- THIS THURSDAY?

15:41.107 --> 15:43.152
- UH-HUH.
WHY PROLONG THE INEVITABLE?

15:43.152 --> 15:44.402
I'M GONNA NEED YOU
OUT ON SATURDAY

15:44.402 --> 15:46.863
SO I CAN SPRAY THE PLACE
WITH INSECTICIDE,

15:46.863 --> 15:48.239
RIP UP THIS PISS CARPET,

15:48.239 --> 15:49.741
AND, YOU KNOW,
MAKE IT LIVABLE.

15:49.741 --> 15:51.117
BOYS, START UPSTAIRS.

15:51.117 --> 15:52.619
- WE'VE GOT KIDS
LIVING HERE,

15:52.619 --> 15:54.038
AND YOU'RE JUST GONNA
THROW US OUT?

15:54.038 --> 15:55.663
HOW DO YOU SLEEP AT NIGHT?

15:55.663 --> 15:58.166
- DON'T BLAME YOUR MISERABLE
GODDAMN LIVES ON ME.

16:03.296 --> 16:05.965
[indistinct chatter]

16:08.385 --> 16:10.595
- OKAY, LISTEN UP.

16:10.595 --> 16:13.057
SOME OF YOU HAVE INQUIRED
ABOUT OUR PETITION.

16:13.057 --> 16:15.642
WE HAVE DEMANDED THAT
LINCOLN GROVE HIGH SCHOOL

16:15.642 --> 16:17.102
OFFER PROGRAMS
FOR SPECIAL STUDENTS

16:17.102 --> 16:19.145
TO HELP THEM FIT IN
WITH THEIR CLASSMATES.

16:19.145 --> 16:20.772
[applause]

16:20.772 --> 16:24.025
- AREN'T YOU GLAD WE CAME?
- YEAH.

16:24.025 --> 16:27.862
- GREAT, ALSO CONCERNING
THE "R" WORD,

16:27.862 --> 16:29.823
WE HAVE DEMANDED
A SCHOOL POLICY

16:29.823 --> 16:32.242
FORBIDDING STUDENTS AND FACULTY
FROM USING THAT WORD.

16:32.242 --> 16:34.661
- RETARD.
- EXCUSE ME.

16:34.661 --> 16:37.872
- RETARD.
YOU CAN'T EVEN SAY IT.

16:37.872 --> 16:41.042
SO HOW DO WE TALK ABOUT IT?

16:41.042 --> 16:44.046
- WE ALL KNOW YOUR OPINION
ON THIS, JEREMY.

16:44.046 --> 16:47.132
BUT RIGHT NOW
I'M THE ONE SPEAKING.

16:47.132 --> 16:48.591
- BROTHERS AND SISTERS,

16:48.591 --> 16:52.512
WORDS ONLY HAVE POWER
IF WE GIVE THEM POWER.

16:52.512 --> 16:57.642
WE MUST TAKE BACK
THE WORD "RETARD."

16:57.642 --> 16:59.644
MAKE IT OURS.

16:59.644 --> 17:02.772
- SWEETHEART, THE REST OF US
FIND THE WORD OFFENSIVE.

17:02.772 --> 17:05.150
- I'M NOT YOUR SWEETHEART,
BITCH.

17:05.150 --> 17:06.233
[all gasp]

17:06.233 --> 17:08.153
- MRS. KANDAGE,
I KNOW YOU MEAN WELL,

17:08.153 --> 17:09.737
BUT MANY OF US HERE
THINK IT'S TIME

17:09.737 --> 17:13.242
THAT WE RECLAIM
AND REDEFINE THE WORD.

17:13.242 --> 17:15.326
AND SINCE NORMIES
DON'T GET CALLED "RETARD,"

17:15.326 --> 17:17.287
THEY DON'T HAVE
A SAY IN THIS.

17:17.287 --> 17:19.497
- NORMIES DO NOT GET A SAY.

17:19.497 --> 17:21.165
- WHAT'S A "NORMIE?"

17:21.165 --> 17:22.834
- I THINK IT'S SLANG
FOR NON-RETARDS.

17:22.834 --> 17:25.462
- HEY, FABIO, DO YOU MIND?
- SORRY.

17:25.462 --> 17:27.422
- I DON'T CARE HOW IT'S USED.

17:27.422 --> 17:29.799
I DON'T WANT ANYBODY CALLING
MY SON THAT WORD EVER.

17:29.799 --> 17:31.050
IT'S INCREDIBLY HURTFUL.

17:31.050 --> 17:32.927
- EVEN IF WE DID GET RID OF IT,

17:32.927 --> 17:35.305
SOMEONE WILL JUST THINK UP
ANOTHER WAY OF SAYING IT.

17:35.305 --> 17:37.307
- THAT'S RIGHT.
THE QUEERS TOOK BACK THEIR WORD.

17:37.307 --> 17:39.726
- IT'S DIFFERENT.
- HOW IS IT DIFFERENT?

17:39.726 --> 17:41.311
IT'S NOT LIKE
RACE ISSUES DISAPPEAR

17:41.311 --> 17:42.437
IF PEOPLE STOP SAYING NIGGER.

17:42.437 --> 17:43.521
- SHUT THE FUCK UP!

17:43.521 --> 17:44.898
I CAN SAY IT, YOU CAN'T.

17:44.898 --> 17:47.233
- RETARDS,
WE MUST BAN TOGETHER.

17:47.233 --> 17:50.153
- THE WAY TO GET RESPECT
IS TO TAKE RESPECT,

17:50.153 --> 17:52.114
AND NORMIES CAN HELP US
GET THAT MESSAGE OUT.

17:52.114 --> 17:54.199
RAISE YOUR HAND
IF YOU'RE WITH US!

17:54.199 --> 17:57.118
- YEAH.

17:57.118 --> 17:58.995
- ME-TARD, YOU-TARD,

17:58.995 --> 18:00.497
RETARD NATION.

18:00.497 --> 18:02.874
ME-TARD, YOU-TARD,

18:02.874 --> 18:05.210
RETARD NATION.

18:05.210 --> 18:06.461
all: ME-TARD, YOU-TARD,

18:06.461 --> 18:08.087
RETARD NATION!

18:08.087 --> 18:09.797
ME-TARD, YOU-TARD,

18:09.797 --> 18:11.216
RETARD NATION!

18:11.216 --> 18:14.385
ME-TARD, YOU-TARD,
RETARD NATION!

18:14.385 --> 18:17.680
ME-TARD, YOU-TARD,
RETARD NATION!

18:17.680 --> 18:20.099
ME-TARD, YOU-TARD,
RETARD NATION!

