contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

18:36.158 --> 18:37.242
- YOU DIGGING THAT SMELL?

18:37.242 --> 18:38.785
- DID SOMETHING DIE IN HERE?

18:38.785 --> 18:40.703
- A COUPLE THOUSAND SOMETHINGS.

18:40.703 --> 18:43.207
- IT GETS BETTER AFTER AWHILE.
- HOW?

18:43.207 --> 18:45.167
- YOUR BRAIN
SORT OF SHORT-CIRCUITS,

18:45.167 --> 18:46.876
SHUTS OFF YOUR SENSE OF SMELL.

18:46.876 --> 18:48.711
- TAPE EVERYTHING UP,
GLOVES AND BOOTS.

18:48.711 --> 18:50.713
WE GOT SOLIDS IN THERE TODAY.

18:50.713 --> 18:52.131
- SOLIDS?

18:52.131 --> 18:54.342
- MAGGOTS, ROACHES,
RATS, FLIES.

18:54.342 --> 18:56.303
YOU GOT ROACHES
INSIDE YOUR SUIT

18:56.303 --> 18:58.763
GOING CRAZY, RUNNING ALL OVER
YOUR SHORT HAIRS,

18:58.763 --> 19:00.182
HARD TO FOCUS ON WORK.

19:00.182 --> 19:02.016
- OH MY GOD, OH MY GOD,
OH MY GOD.

19:02.016 --> 19:04.227
- KEEP YOUR MOUTH SHUT,
AND I DON'T MEAN SHUT UP.

19:04.227 --> 19:06.271
I MEAN, DON'T LET ANYTHING
SPLASH IN YOUR MOUTH.

19:09.232 --> 19:11.901
- YOUR GIRLFRIEND
GONNA BE OKAY?

19:14.237 --> 19:16.114
- THANK YOU, EVERYONE,
FOR SHARING.

19:16.114 --> 19:17.240
HAVE A GOOD DAY.

19:17.240 --> 19:21.160
- [groans]

19:21.160 --> 19:22.912
GREAT MEETING.

19:22.912 --> 19:24.872
I JUST NEED TO GET
MY SLIP SIGNED FOR THE COURT.

19:24.872 --> 19:26.249
- OKAY.

19:26.249 --> 19:28.293
LET'S SEE.

19:28.293 --> 19:32.338
I GUESS WE'LL SEE YOU TWICE
A WEEK FOR AT LEAST SIX MONTHS.

19:32.338 --> 19:35.300
KEEP COMING BACK, FRANK.

19:35.300 --> 19:38.220
- AS IF I HAD A FUCKING CHOICE.

19:38.220 --> 19:39.971
- CONGRATULATIONS.
- WHAT?

19:39.971 --> 19:42.056
- I SAID CONGRATULATIONS.

19:42.056 --> 19:44.642
DURING GROUP SHARE YOU SAID
YOU'RE TWO YEARS SOBER,

19:44.642 --> 19:46.185
UNLESS I MISUNDERSTOOD.

19:46.185 --> 19:48.187
- NO, THAT'S RIGHT.
TWO YEARS TODAY.

19:48.187 --> 19:50.357
- OH, ONLY SIX WEEKS FOR ME.

19:50.357 --> 19:51.816
IT HASN'T BEEN EASY.

19:51.816 --> 19:55.028
I WAS DOWNING
CLEANING PRODUCTS, MOUTHWASH.

19:55.028 --> 19:57.155
- YOU EVER TRY STERNO?
- LOVE STERNO.

19:57.155 --> 20:00.158
- IT'S RIDICULOUS
WHAT PASSES FOR ALCOHOLISM

20:00.158 --> 20:01.368
WITH THIS GROUP.

20:01.368 --> 20:02.994
HER TWO-HOUR BLACKOUT?

20:02.994 --> 20:04.871
I MEAN, COME ON.

20:04.871 --> 20:06.497
I BLACKED OUT A YEAR.

20:06.497 --> 20:08.249
AM I WHINING ABOUT IT?

20:08.249 --> 20:11.377
OR THE GUY THAT LOST HIS JOB
AND BANGED HIS SISTER-IN-LAW?

20:11.377 --> 20:14.088
WHERE I COME FROM,
THAT'S FRIDAY NIGHT.

20:14.088 --> 20:16.382
[both chuckle]

20:16.382 --> 20:17.884
- BUT YOU'VE BEEN SOBER
TWO YEARS.

20:17.884 --> 20:19.385
THAT'S AMAZING.

20:19.385 --> 20:21.304
- BUT IT'S BECAUSE
YOU DON'T NEED BOOZE

20:21.304 --> 20:24.140
TO FILL THE GAPING HOLE
IN YOUR LIFE.

20:24.140 --> 20:26.225
IT'S ABOUT BEING
IN THE MOMENT.

20:26.225 --> 20:27.435
A MEATBALL SUB.

20:27.435 --> 20:29.228
A BEARS GAME
ON THE TELEVISION.

20:29.228 --> 20:30.438
SIMPLE PLEASURES.

20:30.438 --> 20:32.482
- SIMPLE PLEASURES, RIGHT.

20:32.482 --> 20:35.276
FRANK,
I'M CHRIS OR CHRISTOPHER.

20:35.276 --> 20:37.236
I HOPE YOU DON'T MIND
IF I ASK.

20:37.236 --> 20:38.863
WOULD YOU BE MY SPONSOR?

20:38.863 --> 20:41.366
- WOULD I--
- SPONSOR ME IN THE PROGRAM.

20:41.366 --> 20:44.243
MY PREVIOUS SPONSOR MOVED OUT
AND WENT TO LEESBURG.

20:44.243 --> 20:45.912
THAT'S IN FLORIDA.

20:45.912 --> 20:48.290
- RIGHT, RIGHT.
BUT HERE'S THE THING.

20:48.290 --> 20:49.666
MUCH AS I'D LOVE TO HELP,

20:49.666 --> 20:53.294
AND INSPIRING
AS I WOULD NO DOUBT BE,

20:53.294 --> 20:56.506
YOUR BEST SPONSOR
IS YOURSELF.

20:56.506 --> 20:58.549
- I UNDERSTAND.

20:58.549 --> 21:00.344
TAKE CARE.

21:04.306 --> 21:07.350
- WAIT.

21:07.350 --> 21:10.395
YOU SAID YOUR LAST SPONSOR
MOVED OUT.

21:10.395 --> 21:11.854
WHAT, HE--
WHAT, HE LIVED WITH YOU?

21:11.854 --> 21:13.357
- YEAH.
- IN A HOUSE?

21:13.357 --> 21:14.691
YOU LIVE IN A HOUSE,
AN APARTMENT, WHAT?

21:14.691 --> 21:16.317
- A HOUSE.

21:16.317 --> 21:19.112
- I'M SORRY, LET ME
INTRODUCE MYSELF PROPERLY.

21:19.112 --> 21:20.530
I'M FRANK GALLAGHER.

21:20.530 --> 21:22.366
TELL ME YOUR NAME AGAIN.

21:22.366 --> 21:23.700
- IT'S CHRIS OR CHRISTOPHER.

21:23.700 --> 21:25.743
- CHRISTOPHER, RIGHT.

21:33.335 --> 21:35.586
- [gags]

21:38.923 --> 21:40.174
I'M GETTING OUT.

21:40.174 --> 21:41.467
I'M GETTING OUT.

21:41.467 --> 21:44.346
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

21:48.975 --> 21:50.560
- I'M SORRY, BUT NO ONE SPEAKING
ENGLISH AS A FIRST LANGUAGE

21:50.560 --> 21:51.561
SHOULD BE DOING THIS JOB.

21:51.561 --> 21:53.355
- THE MONEY'S GOOD.

21:53.355 --> 21:55.064
- NOT THAT GOOD.

21:55.064 --> 21:57.191
- SO MUCH FOR
"YOU, ME, WE."

21:57.191 --> 21:59.026
- I CAN FEEL COCKROACHES
UNDER MY SUIT.

21:59.026 --> 22:00.153
ON MY BACK!
HIT ME ON MY BACK!

22:00.153 --> 22:02.447
HIT ME ON MY--FUCK.

22:06.325 --> 22:08.077
- OH.

22:08.077 --> 22:11.122
OH, HEY, THESE CANDLES
ARE A NICE IDEA.

22:11.122 --> 22:12.915
- MOM BROUGHT 'EM.
- OH, SHE DID?

22:12.915 --> 22:15.334
- JUST LOOK AT ME.

22:15.334 --> 22:17.044
THAT'S IT.

22:17.044 --> 22:18.588
- OH, SHIT.

22:18.588 --> 22:20.173
- YOU'RE A STUD BULL,
AREN'T YOU, BABY?

22:20.173 --> 22:21.507
- OH, YEAH.

22:21.507 --> 22:24.510
- HOLD THAT THOUGHT.
MOM!

22:24.510 --> 22:26.804
JUMP IN BETWEEN US.
HURRY UP.

22:26.804 --> 22:28.973
- WASN'T SURE
WHEN TO BRING THIS UP,

22:28.973 --> 22:32.643
BUT MAYBE I COULD USE
A LITTLE WARM-UP THIS TIME.

22:32.643 --> 22:35.397
- WARMING UP,
LIKE A JOG AROUND THE BLOCK?

22:35.397 --> 22:37.148
'CAUSE IF YOU'RE ASKING KEV
TO GO DOWN ON YOU,

22:37.148 --> 22:39.025
I CAN TELL YOU RIGHT NOW
THAT IS NOT HAPPENING.

22:39.025 --> 22:41.778
- WOMEN ARE MORE LIKELY TO
CONCEIVE IF THEY HAVE AN ORGASM.

22:41.778 --> 22:43.279
I READ IT IN COSMO.

22:43.279 --> 22:45.448
IT PULLS THE SPERM UP INTO--

22:45.448 --> 22:47.200
- THE CONVERSATION IS
NOT HAPPENING ON THIS END,

22:47.200 --> 22:48.493
JUST SAYING.

22:51.496 --> 22:53.664
- HEY, SORRY I BAILED.
- DON'T BE SORRY.

22:53.664 --> 22:56.292
I'M SURE TONS OF GUYS WOULD
LEAVE THEIR GIRLFRIENDS ALONE

22:56.292 --> 22:57.877
TO SHOVEL BLOOD AND SHIT.

22:57.877 --> 22:59.629
- I WENT DOWN TO THE COFFEE
BEANERY AND GOT A JOB.

22:59.629 --> 23:01.423
- HOW MUCH PER HOUR?

23:01.423 --> 23:03.467
- I MEAN, YOU KNOW, NOT
AS MUCH AS THE CLEANING POSSE,

23:03.467 --> 23:05.218
BUT ALL THE COFFEE
YOU CAN DRINK.

23:05.218 --> 23:06.385
- FULL-TIME?
- CLOSE.

23:06.385 --> 23:07.804
- HOW CLOSE?
- PART-TIME.

23:07.804 --> 23:09.722
THERE ARE OPPORTUNITIES
FOR ADVANCEMENT.

23:09.722 --> 23:12.433
THE MANAGER WAS SAYING--

23:14.852 --> 23:17.772
- WE'VE RECONVENED
THE COUSIN PATRICK WAR COUNCIL.

23:17.772 --> 23:19.483
- NO LUCK ON THE LEGAL FRONT?

23:19.483 --> 23:21.400
- NO, IT TURNS OUT
IT'S PRETTY HARD TO PROVE

23:21.400 --> 23:24.529
THAT SOMEONE HAD DEMENTIA
WHEN THEY SIGNED A WILL.

23:24.529 --> 23:26.823
IN OUR CASE,
VERY FUCKING HARD.

23:26.823 --> 23:28.449
- BECAUSE SHE WAS ALREADY DEAD.

23:28.449 --> 23:30.409
- WHAT WAS OPTION TWO AGAIN?
- WE'RE ON THREE NOW.

23:30.409 --> 23:32.286
CONVINCE PATRICK TO BACK OFF.

23:32.286 --> 23:34.413
- OR OPTION FOUR,
KILL PATRICK.

23:34.413 --> 23:39.460
- BACK TO THREE.
CONVINCE HIM HOW?

23:39.460 --> 23:42.547
- WE GET MY BROTHERS TO GO
AROUND AND SCARE HIM A LITTLE.

23:42.547 --> 23:43.631
- NO WAY.

23:43.631 --> 23:45.424
ENOUGH WITH
THE BROTHERS MILKOVICH.

23:45.424 --> 23:46.926
- NOTHING FATAL.

23:46.926 --> 23:48.512
HIT HIM WITH A BAT
A COUPLE OF TIMES,

23:48.512 --> 23:49.846
A LITTLE PISTOL WHIPPING.

23:49.846 --> 23:51.556
THEY'LL WANT $500 FOR IT,

23:51.556 --> 23:53.474
BUT IF I HELP MICKEY
MOVE SOME METH NEXT WEEK,

23:53.474 --> 23:55.226
THEY'LL SETTLE FOR $200.

23:55.226 --> 23:56.769
- THAT'S A DISCOUNT BEATING.

23:56.769 --> 23:57.770
WHAT DO YOU SAY?

23:57.770 --> 23:59.188
- GUYS, WE CAN'T--

23:59.188 --> 24:02.275
- WE NEED A HOUSE.

24:07.572 --> 24:10.324
- NOW IF YOU'LL EXCUSE ME,
I'LL BE SCRAPING BLOOD AND SHIT

24:10.324 --> 24:11.826
FROM UNDER MY FINGERNAILS,

24:11.826 --> 24:13.662
AND THEN I'LL BE AT V'S
GETTING DRUNK,

24:13.662 --> 24:15.788
PRETENDING I DIDN'T JUST
ORDER A HIT ON A RELATIVE.

24:15.788 --> 24:18.666
- ALL RIGHT.

24:22.795 --> 24:24.589
- FRANK, WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

24:24.589 --> 24:26.716
- SHEILA, THIS IS CHRISTOPHER.

24:26.716 --> 24:28.843
AS HIS A.A. SPONSOR,

24:28.843 --> 24:30.761
I'M HELPING HIM TO WALK
THE STRAIGHT AND NARROW.

24:30.761 --> 24:33.389
- WELL, THAT'S NICE, BUT HOW CAN
YOU BE HIS SPONSOR WHEN YOU--

24:33.389 --> 24:35.850
- I SAID TO HIM, "IF YOU'RE
SERIOUS ABOUT RECOVERY,

24:35.850 --> 24:38.687
"YOU'RE GONNA NEED
24-HOUR-A-DAY OVERSIGHT.

24:38.687 --> 24:40.354
I'M JUST GONNA HAVE
TO MOVE IN WITH YOU."

24:40.354 --> 24:41.898
- REALLY?

24:41.898 --> 24:43.983
- THAT FRANK WOULD DO THIS,
DISRUPT HIS OWN LIFE...

24:43.983 --> 24:47.069
- ALL I ASK IN RETURN
IS YOUR SOBRIETY.

24:47.069 --> 24:49.530
HERE, TAKE THIS DOWN
TO YOUR VAN.

24:49.530 --> 24:50.531
- OH!

24:50.531 --> 24:52.283
NICE MEETING YOU.

24:52.283 --> 24:55.202
- OH, NICE TO MEET YOU.

24:55.202 --> 24:57.496
THANK YOU, FRANK.
GREAT JOB.

24:57.496 --> 24:59.999
- NEVER LET IT BE SAID
THAT FRANK GALLAGHER

24:59.999 --> 25:01.709
OUTSTAYS HIS WELCOME.

25:01.709 --> 25:06.297
- KAREN, LOOK WHAT THEY GAVE ME
WHEN I OFFERED TO VOLUNTEER.

25:06.297 --> 25:10.719
PAMPHLETS AND BUTTONS
AND A BANNER AND T-SHIRTS.

25:10.719 --> 25:12.470
WHY DON'T YOU
COME WITH ME TOMORROW?

25:12.470 --> 25:14.388
I'M GONNA HAVE A TABLE
OUTSIDE THE MARKET.

25:14.388 --> 25:17.266
- NO THANKS, MOM.
- CAN I ASK WHY NOT?

25:17.266 --> 25:19.101
- BECAUSE THEY CALL THEMSELVES
RETARD NATION.

25:19.101 --> 25:20.144
IT'S OFFENSIVE.

25:20.144 --> 25:21.687
- NO, WE'RE--WE'RE--

25:21.687 --> 25:24.065
WE'RE CHALLENGING SOCIETY'S
PRECONCEPTIONS.

25:24.065 --> 25:27.193
- THIS IS GENIUS.
"I AM A RETARD."

25:27.193 --> 25:29.571
- YEAH, BUT READ THE BACK.

25:29.571 --> 25:31.656
- "AND PROUD."
I'M GONNA NEED FIVE OF THESE.

25:31.656 --> 25:34.283
A LOT OF RETARDS
AT THE ALIBI.

25:34.283 --> 25:37.828
- FRANK, I'M NOT COMFORTABLE
WITH HOW YOU'RE USING THAT WORD.

25:37.828 --> 25:39.705
- RETARD?
YOU'RE SAYING IT.

25:39.705 --> 25:41.749
- YEAH, BUT YOU DON'T
HAVE DOWN'S SYNDROME.

25:41.749 --> 25:43.250
- NEITHER DO YOU.

25:43.250 --> 25:46.045
- I KNOW, BUT MY INTENT
IS TO DEFEND FREE SPEECH

25:46.045 --> 25:49.006
AND TO FURTHER PUBLIC
AWARENESS AND END HATE.

25:49.006 --> 25:52.802
AND YOUR INTENT
IS SIMPLY TO BE RUDE.

25:52.802 --> 25:55.596
- HELLO?

25:58.265 --> 26:00.726
V?

26:03.521 --> 26:04.606
OH!

26:04.606 --> 26:06.691
UH, OH, SORRY.

26:06.691 --> 26:07.566
OH.

26:07.566 --> 26:09.652
AHH.

26:09.652 --> 26:11.445
UGH, AH.

26:11.445 --> 26:15.241
- THAT THREW ME OFF.
PERISCOPE DOWN.

26:20.621 --> 26:23.207
- HEY.

26:23.207 --> 26:25.793
LOOK, YOU NEED TO BACK OFF
THE GALLAGHER HOUSE.

26:25.793 --> 26:29.005
IF YOU DON'T,
YOU'LL BE SORRY.

26:32.591 --> 26:36.137
- [groans]

26:36.137 --> 26:37.972
- FUCK SAKE.

26:37.972 --> 26:40.599
- A .22?

26:40.599 --> 26:41.642
YOU SURE IT'LL STOP ME?

26:41.642 --> 26:43.602
- YOU WANT TO FIND OUT?

26:43.602 --> 26:44.979
WHAT THE FUCK ARE YOU DOING?

26:44.979 --> 26:46.230
GET UP AND
KNOCK HIM ON HIS ASS.

26:46.230 --> 26:48.482
I GOT HIM COVERED.

26:51.277 --> 26:54.488
- I'D LIKE YOU TO MEET THE WIFE,
ELLEN.

26:55.698 --> 26:57.700
- THEY'RE REMOVING
THE TOILETS.

26:57.700 --> 26:59.493
- I'LL GET SOME BUCKETS.

26:59.493 --> 27:00.870
- I GUESS IT DIDN'T WORK OUT
WITH YOUR BROTHER.

27:00.870 --> 27:02.997
- MANDY, ARE WE GETTING
OUR MONEY BACK?

27:02.997 --> 27:05.667
- MINUS $100.
HE TOOK A CHAIN OFF MICKEY.

27:05.667 --> 27:06.959
- OVER THERE.
BY THE COUCH.

27:06.959 --> 27:08.753
YEAH, JUST LEAVE IT.

27:08.753 --> 27:10.713
- BYE, HONEY, OFF TO WORK.

27:10.713 --> 27:12.840
- WHY IS HE LEAVING
A TOILET IN OUR LIVING ROOM?

27:12.840 --> 27:14.967
- BYE, HONEY!
I'M OFF TO WORK!

27:14.967 --> 27:17.178
- WE ARE SO LOSING THE HOUSE.

27:17.178 --> 27:20.264
- I TOLD YOU WE ARE GOING--
- TO BE FINE, I KNOW.

27:20.264 --> 27:22.850
BUT WILL WE BE FINE HERE
OR SOMEWHERE ELSE?

27:25.686 --> 27:28.272
- THE PROBATE HEARING
IS TOMORROW.

27:28.272 --> 27:29.690
MAYBE WE'LL GET LUCKY.

27:29.690 --> 27:32.443
IF NOT, I WILL FIND US
A PLACE TO LIVE, OKAY?

27:32.443 --> 27:34.528
PLEASE DROP LIAM AT V'S
ON YOUR WAY TO SCHOOL.

27:34.528 --> 27:36.030
EVERYONE ELSE,
GRAB A LUNCH AND HEAD OUT.

27:36.030 --> 27:39.701
NO TRUANT GALLAGHERS TODAY.

27:39.701 --> 27:41.745
[hammers banging]

27:46.874 --> 27:50.044
- YOU KNOW, BEING GUARDIAN
DOESN'T MAKE YOU SUPER-MOM.

27:50.044 --> 27:52.296
- YOU NOTICED.

27:52.296 --> 27:55.800
- I'M JUST SAYING,
IT'S NOT ALL ON YOU.

27:59.595 --> 28:01.722
THANKS.

28:05.976 --> 28:10.189
[drill whirring]

28:10.189 --> 28:11.774
- HOW ARE YOU THIS MORNING?

28:11.774 --> 28:13.859
- NEVER BETTER.

28:13.859 --> 28:16.237
REPLACING THE TOILET
WITH A LOW-FLOW MODEL,

28:16.237 --> 28:17.530
MUCH MORE EFFICIENT.

28:17.530 --> 28:18.781
- I BET IT LOWERS
THE WATER BILL.

28:18.781 --> 28:21.826
- OH, WITHOUT QUESTION.

28:21.826 --> 28:25.538
- PATRICK, WE GOT OFF
ON THE WRONG FOOT.

28:25.538 --> 28:30.126
- SENDING MICKEY MILKOVICH OVER
WITH A BASEBALL BAT, HMM?

28:30.126 --> 28:33.337
IS THAT THE FOOT YOU MEAN?

28:33.337 --> 28:37.759
- IF WE LET YOU TAKE THE HOUSE,
WILL YOU RENT IT TO US?

28:37.759 --> 28:38.843
- SURE.

28:38.843 --> 28:40.970
CALL IT $1,800 A MONTH,

28:40.970 --> 28:43.347
FIRST, LAST, AND DEPOSIT.

28:43.347 --> 28:44.557
- YOU KNOW WE DON'T HAVE
THAT KIND OF--

28:44.557 --> 28:46.058
- NO?

28:46.058 --> 28:50.688
I THOUGHT LIVING IN SQUALOR
WAS A LIFESTYLE CHOICE.

28:54.776 --> 28:56.694
- IT'S JUST THAT WHEN WE FIRST
STARTED THIS WITH MOM,

28:56.694 --> 28:58.571
WE APPROACHED IT
LIKE A MEDICAL PROCEDURE,

28:58.571 --> 28:59.989
BUT THESE LAST FEW TIMES,
IS IT ME

28:59.989 --> 29:01.323
OR WAS SHE ACTING
LIKE SHE WAS ON A DATE?

29:01.323 --> 29:03.117
- SHE ALWAYS DRESSES NICE.

29:03.117 --> 29:04.869
- MUSK PERFUME,
GOLD TIPS.

29:04.869 --> 29:06.954
WHEN HAS SHE EVER WORN GOLD TIPS
TO OUR HOUSE, KEV?

29:06.954 --> 29:08.747
- LIKE I'D NOTICE.

29:08.747 --> 29:09.874
- SO YOU HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT I'M TALKING ABOUT?

29:09.874 --> 29:12.543
- BABY, MAYBE SHE MADE
AN EXTRA EFFORT.

29:12.543 --> 29:14.044
- AHA!

29:14.044 --> 29:15.588
- WHAT'S WRONG WITH THAT?

29:15.588 --> 29:18.549
- LOW-CUT DRESS,
"FUCK-ME" PUMPS.

29:18.549 --> 29:21.177
- MAYBE SHE'S EXCITED
TO HAVE A GRANDCHILD,

29:21.177 --> 29:23.470
WANTS ME TO BE
PROPERLY MOTIVATED.

29:23.470 --> 29:24.763
- AND THAT DOESN'T
FREAK YOU OUT?

29:24.763 --> 29:26.098
- THIS WHOLE THING
FREAKS ME OUT,

29:26.098 --> 29:28.517
AND I'M TRYING
NOT TO THINK ABOUT IT.

29:28.517 --> 29:30.394
I'M LIKE
A PROFESSIONAL ATHLETE.

29:30.394 --> 29:33.105
IF I THINK, IT AFFECTS
MY PERFORMANCE.

29:33.105 --> 29:37.318
MY JOB IS TO NOT THINK.

29:48.329 --> 29:52.583
- FUCK! FUCK!

29:57.004 --> 29:58.672
IF YOU'RE GONNA
FOLLOW ME TO WORK,

29:58.672 --> 30:00.216
HOW ABOUT GIVING ME A RIDE?

30:00.216 --> 30:01.634
- NOT YOUR CHAUFFEUR, BRO.

30:01.634 --> 30:03.385
DON'T BURN THE MILK.

30:03.385 --> 30:04.803
IT'S NOT GOOD
WHEN YOU BURN IT.

30:04.803 --> 30:06.847
- JIM!

30:06.847 --> 30:11.019
ANDY FROM MED SCHOOL.

30:11.019 --> 30:12.853
I'M AT COUNTY GENERAL
DOWN THE STREET.

30:12.853 --> 30:14.813
- NO KIDDING.

30:14.813 --> 30:18.026
GOOD TO SEE YOU.

30:18.026 --> 30:21.820
- I LOVE THIS PLACE.
GREAT COFFEE.

30:21.820 --> 30:23.907
YOU'RE A WORKING MAN NOW, HUH?

30:23.907 --> 30:25.824
- OH, MANAGEMENT TRAINEE.

30:25.824 --> 30:27.911
YOU KNOW, THEY WON'T LET YOU
BUY A FRANCHISE

30:27.911 --> 30:28.994
TILL YOU RUN
ONE OF THEIR STORES.

30:28.994 --> 30:30.287
- NICE.

30:30.287 --> 30:34.208
I HEAR THESE PLACES
ARE A GOLD MINE.

30:34.208 --> 30:36.502
- WHAT CAN I GET YOU, MAN?

30:36.502 --> 30:39.380
- HEY, YOU KNOW ADAM BRITT,
NICK STATHIS, MARK?

30:39.380 --> 30:42.508
THEY'RE ALL DOING
RESIDENCIES IN CHICAGO.

30:42.508 --> 30:44.510
NICK'S ORTHO,
MARK'S A SURGEON.

30:44.510 --> 30:46.053
WE'RE GRABBING DINNER
TOMORROW NIGHT.

30:46.053 --> 30:47.263
YOU SHOULD JOIN US.

30:47.263 --> 30:48.347
- YEAH, SOUNDS FUN.

30:48.347 --> 30:49.848
BUT I'M NOT SURE IF I CAN.

30:49.848 --> 30:52.935
- THEY WOULD LOVE TO SEE YOU.
YOU GOTTA COME.

30:56.689 --> 31:01.277
UM, DOUBLE CAPPUCCINO
WITH NON-FAT.

31:09.243 --> 31:11.078
- I WAS GONNA WAIT
FOR THE LANDLORD,

31:11.078 --> 31:13.998
BUT SOMEBODY ALREADY
KICKED THE DOOR IN FOR US.

31:13.998 --> 31:17.126
- THAT'S CONSIDERATE.

31:17.126 --> 31:18.752
- AT LEAST
IT'S IN OUR PRICE RANGE.

31:18.752 --> 31:20.462
- BARELY.

31:20.462 --> 31:23.091
- WELL, IT'S NOT LIKE WE LIVE
IN THE GOLD COAST NOW.

31:23.091 --> 31:26.010
PLACE JUST NEEDS SOME PAINT,
A CASE OF ROACH MOTELS.

31:26.010 --> 31:27.971
DOWN THE ROAD,
MAYBE WE SAVE SOME MONEY

31:27.971 --> 31:31.890
AND FIND A HOUSE
BACK IN OUR OLD HOOD.

31:31.890 --> 31:33.392
- NEED A CRACK PIPE?

31:33.392 --> 31:35.102
- BETTER NOT TOUCH THAT.

31:35.102 --> 31:37.563
- TOUCH IT?
I'M READY TO SMOKE OUT OF IT.

31:41.150 --> 31:44.570
I GUESS I'LL CALL THE LANDLORD
AND TELL HIM WE'LL TAKE IT.

31:52.036 --> 31:54.538
- [retches]

32:02.212 --> 32:04.132
- I NEED YOU TO WATCH
YOUR BABY BROTHER.

32:04.132 --> 32:05.799
AND WHO'S THAT PUKING
ON HIS TIMBERLANDS?

32:05.799 --> 32:07.343
- COUSIN PATRICK.

32:07.343 --> 32:10.137
HE'S GOT NAUSEA,
SHORTNESS OF BREATH,

32:10.137 --> 32:14.933
BLOOD IN URINE,
SEVERE ILLNESS, AND DEATH.

32:14.933 --> 32:16.352
- WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU READING?

32:16.352 --> 32:20.023
- RAT POISON.

32:24.193 --> 32:25.944
- HI! HI!

32:25.944 --> 32:28.072
WE ARE RETARD NATION.

32:28.072 --> 32:30.158
YEAH, WE'RE
A LOCAL ORGANIZATION,

32:30.158 --> 32:32.951
BUT AS THE NAME SUGGESTS,
WE ARE GOING NATIONAL.

32:32.951 --> 32:35.996
WE'RE PROMOTING THE IDEA
THAT PEOPLE WITH DOWN'S SYNDROME

32:35.996 --> 32:38.041
NEED TO RECLAIM
THEIR OWN IDENTITIES

32:38.041 --> 32:40.125
IN ORDER TO DEFINE THEMSELVES.

32:40.125 --> 32:43.045
SO IF YOU'D LIKE TO,
YOU CAN MAKE A DONATION

32:43.045 --> 32:44.755
OR IF YOU'D LIKE TO BUY
A T-SHIRT OR JUST GET SIGNED--

32:44.755 --> 32:46.423
- WHAT THE HELL IS THIS?

32:46.423 --> 32:49.385
- WELL, WE'RE A LOCAL
ORGANIZATION, RETARD NATION--

32:49.385 --> 32:50.969
- TAKE IT DOWN NOW.

32:50.969 --> 32:52.721
- SIR, I'M AFRAID
I CAN'T DO THAT.

32:52.721 --> 32:54.014
- LADY, YOU'RE NOT GONNA STAND
IN FRONT OF MY MARKET

32:54.014 --> 32:55.641
WITH THIS GODDAMN SIGN.

32:55.641 --> 32:57.267
PACK IT UP NOW OR I'LL DO IT,
ALL RIGHT?

32:57.267 --> 33:02.398
- SIR, WE WILL NOT
BE INTIMIDATED BY NORMIES.

33:02.398 --> 33:04.983
- BY WHAT?
- BY NORMIES.

33:04.983 --> 33:06.527
- GODDAMN IT,
GET THIS CRAP OUT OF HERE.

33:06.527 --> 33:07.945
- DON'T!
- ALL OF IT.

33:07.945 --> 33:09.238
MA'AM, I'M VERY SORRY--
- DON'T!

33:09.238 --> 33:11.824
- DO NOT TOUCH ME
IN FRONT OF MY MARKET.

33:11.824 --> 33:13.659
THIS IS HATE SPEECH.
GET YOUR HANDS OFF OF ME.

33:13.659 --> 33:16.328
- ME-TARD, YOU-TARD,
RETARD NATION.

33:19.790 --> 33:21.333
- SO THIS IS IT.

33:21.333 --> 33:26.880
IT'S ONLY A ONE-BEDROOM,
BUT I'M AT WORK A LOT.

33:26.880 --> 33:28.924
- CHRISTOPHER.
- YEAH, FRANK?

33:28.924 --> 33:31.218
- IN ORDER
FOR THE HEALING TO BEGIN,

33:31.218 --> 33:33.054
IT'S IMPORTANT
THAT YOU BE HONEST

33:33.054 --> 33:34.805
AND TELL ME
WHERE YOU HIDE YOUR BOOZE.

33:34.805 --> 33:36.223
UNDER THE CUSHIONS?
BACK OF THE CLOSET?

33:36.223 --> 33:37.641
I KNOW ALL THE TRICKS.

33:37.641 --> 33:40.144
- I THREW IT OUT.

33:40.144 --> 33:43.147
- DO YOU MIND IF I LOOK AROUND
IN CASE YOU MISSED A BOTTLE?

33:43.147 --> 33:45.482
- YEAH, YEAH, THAT'S SMART.

33:45.482 --> 33:47.025
- WHERE DO YOU WORK?

33:47.025 --> 33:48.944
- I'M A VET TECH FOR THE CITY.

33:48.944 --> 33:50.946
I DEAL WITH
STRAY CATS AND DOGS.

33:50.946 --> 33:52.656
- MEANING YOU KILL THEM?

33:52.656 --> 33:55.617
- IN VETERINARY PARLANCE,
IT'S CALLED "CONTROL."

33:55.617 --> 33:58.871
SOMETIMES I RESCUE
A BEAUTY LIKE BESSIE THERE.

33:58.871 --> 34:01.957
IT MAKES ME FEEL BETTER
ABOUT IT ALL.

34:01.957 --> 34:04.418
HEY, I'VE GOT
A SURPRISE FOR YOU.

34:04.418 --> 34:06.170
WHY DON'T I GRAB IT?

34:06.170 --> 34:08.839
- WHAT SORT OF SURPRISE?
- YOU'LL SEE!

34:16.013 --> 34:17.889
- HEY.

34:23.312 --> 34:25.731
YOU KNOW YOUR DOG IS DEAD,
RIGHT?

34:25.731 --> 34:30.194
- TAXIDERMY
IS A HOBBY OF MINE.

34:30.194 --> 34:33.197
- [sighs]

34:33.197 --> 34:35.991
SO WHEN YOU SAY RESCUE,

34:35.991 --> 34:37.743
YOU MEAN BRING THEM HOME
AND STUFF THEM,

34:37.743 --> 34:39.328
BECAUSE MOST PEOPLE
WHEN THEY USED THAT WORD--

34:39.328 --> 34:41.496
- MEATBALL SUBS!

34:41.496 --> 34:44.208
LIKE YOU SAID, REMEMBER?

34:44.208 --> 34:45.250
SIMPLE PLEASURES.

34:45.250 --> 34:46.585
LIVING IN THE MOMENT.

34:46.585 --> 34:48.170
- SOUNDS LIKE SOMETHING
I WOULD SAY.

34:48.170 --> 34:50.172
- YOU MENTIONED
YOU'RE A BEARS FAN.

34:50.172 --> 34:52.382
THERE'S NO GAME ON, BUT I'VE GOT
LAST SEASON'S HIGHLIGHTS.

34:52.382 --> 34:55.136
YOU EAT, I'LL CUE IT UP.

34:57.179 --> 34:58.263
YOU WANT A BLANKET?

34:58.263 --> 35:00.724
IT'S KIND OF CHILLY.

35:02.601 --> 35:04.853
- I HAVE A NEW RESPECT
FOR BARISTAS.

35:04.853 --> 35:06.230
IT TURNS OUT IT'S
A HIGHLY DEMANDING CRAFT.

35:06.230 --> 35:07.731
WHO KNEW?

35:07.731 --> 35:09.107
YOU KEEP BURNING THE SHIT
OUT OF YOUR--

35:09.107 --> 35:11.068
WHAT'S UP?

35:11.068 --> 35:13.278
- TELL HIM.

35:13.278 --> 35:17.241
- I KILLED PATRICK.

35:17.241 --> 35:18.992
- WHAT?

35:32.339 --> 35:34.174
- OPTION FOUR: KILL PATRICK.

35:34.174 --> 35:35.968
WHY SKIP AN OPTION?

35:35.968 --> 35:37.803
- THE WHOLE LIFE IN PRISON
THING, SWEETHEART.

35:37.803 --> 35:40.931
- I REALIZE YOU'VE HAD SKETCHY
PARENTAL ROLE MODELS, OKAY?

35:40.931 --> 35:42.808
BUT AS YOUR
NEWLY APPOINTED GUARDIAN,

35:42.808 --> 35:44.977
CAN WE AGREE THAT
OFFING PEOPLE IS NOT COOL?

35:44.977 --> 35:46.395
CAN WE GET ON
THE SAME PAGE WITH THAT?

35:46.395 --> 35:48.355
- YEAH.

35:48.355 --> 35:50.233
- IF THIS COMES BACK TO US,

35:50.233 --> 35:52.067
IF WE GET CHARGED
WITH HOMICIDE,

35:52.067 --> 35:55.821
DO YOU REALIZE
HOW SERIOUS THAT IS?

35:55.821 --> 35:57.365
WHAT?

35:57.365 --> 35:59.575
- LIAM.

35:59.575 --> 36:02.160
