38:04.783 --> 38:07.786
- PLEASE, FRANK,
PLEASE, DON'T MOVE OUT.

38:07.786 --> 38:10.455
EVERYTHING IS GOING
SO GOOD WITH US.

38:10.455 --> 38:12.499
I WON'T LIE TO YOU AGAIN.

38:12.499 --> 38:14.251
I PROMISE.

38:14.251 --> 38:15.585
