42:40.183 --> 42:42.394
- THINK I WOULD LIE
ABOUT THAT?

42:42.394 --> 42:44.813
- WELL, WHY NOT?

42:44.813 --> 42:50.402
IT'LL MAKE EVERYONE FEEL BAD
FOR YOU, LOWER THEIR GUARD.

42:50.402 --> 42:55.699
POOR KAREN, BACK HOME
WITH HER TAIL BETWEEN HER LEGS.

42:55.699 --> 42:57.618
- THAT'S RIGHT.

42:57.618 --> 43:01.496
