YOU LOST YOUR TOUCH.

43:22.434 --> 43:24.853
- WHAT DO YOU WANT?

43:24.853 --> 43:28.732
- TAKE YOUR CLOTHES OFF.

43:28.732 --> 43:31.026
[horns honking]

