44:38.551 --> 44:41.764
[moaning]

44:43.723 --> 44:45.850
- KAREN, HONEY,
CAN YOU COME DOWN?

44:45.850 --> 44:48.686
- DON'T STOP.
- I WASN'T PLANNING ON IT.

44:48.686 --> 44:51.481
- KAREN,
MRS. WONG IS HERE.

44:51.481 --> 44:53.066
OH, COME ON IN.

44:53.066 --> 44:56.152
- TIMMY SAW YOU
AT THE SUPERMARKET.

44:56.152 --> 44:59.948
- OH, OH, THAT'S JUST MY
VOLUNTEER WORK FOR HYMIE'S SAKE.

44:59.948 --> 45:02.826
- YOU HAVE TO STOP THAT SHIT.
