45:02.826 --> 45:04.327
- TIMMY SAW YOU FIGHT
WITH THAT MAN.

45:04.327 --> 45:05.870
HE'S EMBARRASSED FOR YOU.

45:05.870 --> 45:08.164
- WELL, I DON'T KNOW
IF IT'S A CULTURAL THING

45:08.164 --> 45:10.918
