- DON'T TOUCH ME.

49:23.586 --> 49:25.296
- I COULD BE YOUR SPONSOR.
I'M NOT A DRINKER,

49:25.296 --> 49:26.964
BUT I'VE BEEN TO SO MANY
MEETINGS, I KNOW THE PROCEDURE.

49:26.964 --> 49:29.092
- NO!
NO, NO, THANK YOU.

49:29.092 --> 49:31.969
- I'M SORRY
IF I FREAKED YOU OUT.

49:31.969 --> 49:37.308
I'M NOT REAL GOOD WITH,
WELL, WITH PEOPLE, REALLY.

49:37.308 --> 49:39.769
IT WAS GREAT
HAVING SOMEONE TO TALK TO.

49:39.769 --> 49:42.522
- GET A ROOM, ASSHOLES.

49:42.522 --> 49:44.357
- I'M SORRY, FRANK.

49:44.357 --> 49:46.068
