YOU WANT TO HAVE SEX WITH ME,

50:02.667 --> 50:05.628
I GUESS I'D DO MY BEST.

50:05.628 --> 50:08.881
- WHAT HAPPENED
TO YOUR OLD SPONSOR?

50:08.881 --> 50:11.093
- EITHER HE'S IN FLORIDA,

50:11.093 --> 50:13.803
OR HE'S AVOIDING ME,
THINKS I'M CREEPY,

50:13.803 --> 50:16.222
BEING CLINGY AND ALL,
AND LONELY.

50:16.222 --> 50:21.018
- SO BASICALLY
THE PROBLEM IS YOU'RE CLINGY.

50:21.018 --> 50:23.271
WHAT'S FOR DINNER
AT YOUR PLACE?

50:23.271 --> 50:25.022
- RIB EYES.

50:25.022 --> 50:26.649
- BUT WE STOP AT THE LIQUOR
STORE, AND YOU'RE PAYING?

50:26.649 --> 50:28.901
- ANYTHING YOU WANT.
- LET'S GO.

50:28.901 --> 50:31.195
- REALLY?
YOU MEAN IT?

50:31.195 --> 50:34.031
- OH, CLINGY
IS A WALK IN THE PARK.

50:34.031 --> 50:38.245
HERE, HAVE IT.

50:38.245 --> 50:40.080
I REALLY LIKE HER.
- YEAH?

50:40.080 --> 50:41.289
- SHE'S A POET.

50:47.962 --> 50:49.088
- KAREN.

50:49.088 --> 50:52.175
- OH, MOM,
YOU SCARED ME.

50:52.175 --> 50:55.386
- YOU TOLD ME YOU
CAME HOME TO BE WITH HYMIE,

50:55.386 --> 50:59.807
BUT YOU TOLD THE WONGS
TO COME TAKE HYMIE.

50:59.807 --> 51:02.560
WHY WOULD YOU DO THAT?

51:04.312 --> 51:08.065
- I MISSED YOU, MOM.

51:10.485 --> 51:12.904
- SO IT'S TRUE.

51:12.904 --> 51:16.073
- EVERYTHING WAS BETTER
BEFORE HYMIE CAME ALONG,

51:16.073 --> 51:19.452
JUST YOU AND ME.

51:19.452 --> 51:24.081
I WANTED US BACK.

51:24.081 --> 51:26.167
I LOVE YOU.

51:31.298 --> 51:32.340
- YOU'RE SHITTING ME.

51:32.340 --> 51:34.134
- STANDARD POLICE PROCEDURE,
SIR.

51:34.134 --> 51:35.301
WE'LL HAVE TO MEET
THE SEX CRIMES DETECTIVES

51:35.301 --> 51:37.137
AT THE STATION, UNLESS--
- UNLESS WHAT?

51:37.137 --> 51:41.140
- THE CHARGES ARE DROPPED.
- CHARGES ARE--?

51:41.140 --> 51:43.518
- 400 A MONTH RENT,
NO DEPOSIT.

51:43.518 --> 51:45.102
- ARE YOU IN ON THIS?

51:45.102 --> 51:46.687
- I'M NOT IN ON ANYTHING,
SIR.

51:46.687 --> 51:48.356
I AM, HOWEVER, GONNA MAKE
A RADIO CALL FROM THE CAR.

51:51.234 --> 51:54.445
- YOU CAN TAKE YOUR 400
AND SHOVE IT UP YOUR ASS.

51:54.445 --> 51:58.366
- I REMEMBER YOUR HANDS
TOUCHING ME AND--

51:58.366 --> 51:59.784
- $1,200.

51:59.784 --> 52:03.205
- YOU SAID IT WAS
OUR LITTLE SECRET.

52:03.205 --> 52:06.208
I KNEW IT WAS WRONG.

52:06.208 --> 52:07.500
- JESUS, WHAT--

52:07.500 --> 52:09.293
900, FINAL OFFER.

52:09.293 --> 52:11.170
- 500, NO DEPOSIT.

52:11.170 --> 52:13.798
I NEED A 50-YEAR LEASE,
AND I WANT THAT IN WRITING.

52:13.798 --> 52:17.343
