A LOT OF LIGHT IN.

52:49.208 --> 52:51.168
- THANKS.

52:51.168 --> 52:53.838
- NIGHT, FRANK.
- GOOD NIGHT, CHRISTOPHER.

53:03.097 --> 53:04.724
